products.name: Complete Fixed Home Loan Package
products.description: The Complete Fixed Home Loan Package includes a fixed home loan, up to 9 offset accounts, a credit card and other good stuff - including our great rates.

products.name: Complete Variable Home Loan Package
products.description: Home loans don't have to be so rigid. This flexible package has up to nine offset accounts, a credit card and other good stuff - including our great rates.

products.name: Regular Saver Home Loan
products.description: The Regular Saver Home Loan is a variable rate home loan. The product is available for both owner occupied and investment purposes (the loan amount will be restricted by your property value, repayment type and loan purpose). Plus you can link an optional offset facility to your loan to help reduce your interest and pay off your loan faster.

products.name: Mortgage Shredder Home Loan
products.description: The Mortgage Shredder Home Loan is a variable rate home loan available for both owner occupied and investment purposes (the loan amount will be restricted by your property value, repayment type and loan purpose). Plus you can link an optional offset facility to your loan to help reduce your interest and pay off your loan faster.

products.name: Premium Select Home Loan
products.description: The Premium Select Home Loan is a variable rate home loan with a discount off the standard variable rate. The product is available for both owner occupied and investment purposes when borrowing up to 90% of the property value. Plus you can link an optional offset facility to your loan to help reduce your interest and pay off your loan faster.

products.name: Fixed Rate Home Loan
products.description: The Fixed Rate Home Loan lets you lock in a competitive fixed rate for one to five years, and enjoy the peace of mind that comes with consistent repayments. The loan is available for both owner occupied and investment purposes (the loan amount will be restricted by your property value, repayment type and loan purpose). Plus link an optional offset facility to your loan to help reduce your interest and pay off your loan faster. After the expiry of your fixed rate term your Home Loan will revert to the Mortgage Shredder Home Loan.

products.name: Gold Term Deposit
products.description: The Gold Term Deposit lets you lock in a competitive fixed rate for a range of periods from one month to five years. It's available to customers aged 12 or over, and can be set up at a Bankwest branch.

products.name: Business Low Rate Loan
products.description: The Business Low Rate Loan is a lending facility offering a competitive variable interest rate, flexible terms and a range of security options such as residential, commercial and/or rural properties. Loan funds are for the purpose of capital acquisition or investment in your business.

products.name: Business Fixed Rate Loan
products.description: The Bankwest Business Fixed Rate Loan allows for interest to be fixed for up to 5 years. Funds are for the purpose of capital acquisition or investment in your business. This account allows interest to be raised monthly, quarterly, half yearly or annually. Choose from interest only or principal and interest repayment options.

products.name: Online Term Deposit
